{"tid":1492940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝大陸律師點醒文宣組 呢一場係護法之役","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T01:01:14.000Z","uid":42691,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d37ae5ca0b1494d0baa41a6466162cfc4b373045","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GUuOhdR8Uo0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGUuOhdR8Uo0&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41AxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=69cde1c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=GUuOhdR8Uo0</a><br />\n<br />\n各位文宣巴絲<br />\n「法律之爭」係對大陸文宣重要方向<br />\n<br />\n政治紛爭/獨立係大陸抹黑<br />\n係一場法律問題之爭<br />\n係護法之役<br />\n陳秋實既出現<br />\n以及「法律之爭」既論調<br />\n對輸出革命 拉攏大陸民心有極大幫助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">最後希望佢冇事<br />\n好人通常都冇好下場<br />\n佢最尾笑得好勉強<br />\n香港呢次輸咗都會變地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9c95d1562c0786211eaeb6bc4baff50418db6a70","tid":1492940,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abc85101da0a771ef36e9bcbf24e874d5cc90a04","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f353ca8805fe68f1e26cadd564f9d16684efb4b","tid":1492940,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:41:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b14fc8f72417f372e631a74fb7469da297d65d","tid":1492940,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a08596a052747e07ad2c72a24dbe3d87a550dc08","tid":1492940,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qcHPrs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qcHPrs.jpg&h=93b2cd8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6y7ApZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y7ApZO.jpg&h=ad344a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PPSsc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PPSsc9.jpg&h=d17b6283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgEK2Mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgEK2Mv.jpg&h=a4309f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uUVqNdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuUVqNdb.jpg&h=d00fdf30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VadDnMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVadDnMx.jpg&h=8b915084&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb2338c519b44c5cb34e5be08b6315475d464bc9","tid":1492940,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"國師之前都講係香港憲法保護戰, 而唔係咩反送中"},{"pid":"ed355612622313f65556ebf798e155a3e533b24e","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb2338c519b44c5cb34e5be08b6315475d464bc9","tid":1492940,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"國師之前都講係香港憲法保護戰, 而唔係咩反送中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"不謀而合<br />\n停留係修例運動、反送中運動<br />\n唔足以概括做緊既野"},{"pid":"caf7483e4ed4d966bd62afd1ff5f66e3b28302c1","tid":1492940,"uid":115069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6b0af2c3806eaaccfbf1c890b449d8e669691aac","tid":1492940,"uid":287096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"719757cbe9f89c9d0af14ba1f7b9e6d255641e56","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb2338c519b44c5cb34e5be08b6315475d464bc9","tid":1492940,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"國師之前都講係香港憲法保護戰, 而唔係咩反送中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"btw有冇link 好文共賞"},{"pid":"53f926925ec342e2c666ae3e3db5f12da16c0940","tid":1492940,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"719757cbe9f89c9d0af14ba1f7b9e6d255641e56","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb2338c519b44c5cb34e5be08b6315475d464bc9","tid":1492940,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"國師之前都講係香港憲法保護戰, 而唔係咩反送中"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"btw有冇link 好文共賞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:02:18.000Z","msg":"開心share<br />\n其實都講左一段時間 但慣性太大 一直改唔到口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港憲法保衛戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1208298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1208298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de887516283d4ab6c027db8b92221f1f6240ed20","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"陳雲：這次是香港憲法保衛戰，是護法之戰。不是什麼「反送中」。「反送中」是泛民的行動口號，越叫你越恐懼，令你恐懼共產黨，令你恐懼去大陸，好似豬仔恐懼被人送人屠房那樣，行動只是產生更多的恐懼，而且「送中」與「送終」同音，是要香港人自我咀咒，要自己仆街陷家鏟送終買棺材。<br />\n「反送中」是單一議程的yes or no的戰鬥，一旦條例通過，你就是戰敗。你自己定義好自己接受戰敗的日程，目前是六月二十日，下個星期四，你就戰敗。<br />\n香港憲法保衛戰，是理直氣壯的、正面增強能力的持續行動。我是保衛憲法，保衛香港的獨立司法管轄權（即是香港的國界），你即使通過了逃犯引渡條例修訂，我也繼續保衛憲法，鬥爭下去。而香港人反對單程證制度、反對大灣區、反對中港融合，也是在保衛憲法，這個口號可以化作更大的戰場。即使香港建國了，我們也要繼續保衛憲法，因為憲政民主就是恆久的警惕。It's not yes or no for one time. It's forever yes, I do. 一群在建國的國民的心靈，好似結婚的誓詞。<br />\n再者，就是這個口號的安全性，日後也可以植入港共的基本法教育。香港人在保衛基本法而已，基本法是共產黨送給香港的、弄假成真的小憲法，共產黨有什麼可以說呢？<br />\n用詞正確，大方大氣，就是《春秋》大義，名正言順，香港人做大事。"},{"pid":"57317bedb60d4947325984ea9bc86586e8200e59","tid":1492940,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6305802fb7e038920d60477c0d397a28b3658113","tid":1492940,"uid":63206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:01:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">阻阻大家 幫手簽同share！叫紐西蘭政府支持香港同關注香港人人權問題！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.parliament.nz/en/pb/petitions/document/PET_90982/petition-of-serena-lee-address-the-violation-of-human\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.nz%2Fen%2Fpb%2Fpetitions%2Fdocument%2FPET_90982%2Fpetition-of-serena-lee-address-the-violation-of-human&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41AxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=08f9d8cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.parliament.nz/en/pb/petitions/document/PET_90982/petition-of-serena-lee-address-the-violation-of-human</a>"}]}